l.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Norah-Jones-Dave-Grohl-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Norah-Jones-Dave-Grohl-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Norah-Jones-Dave-Grohl-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Norah-Jones-Dave-Grohl-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Norah-Jones-Dave-Grohl-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl)</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/norah-jones">诺拉·琼斯 (Norah Jones)</a>一起在她的播客上播放了一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">《喷火战机》的</a>稀有曲目 - 请听下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/foo-fighters-cover-interview-2021-medicine-at-midnight-2872365">喷火战机：“我们的联系超越了音乐”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位喷火战机主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/norah-jones-4-1300579">此前曾与这位爵士歌手合作</a>过歌曲“Virginia Moon”，该歌曲出现在 2005 年专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-7661-303899">In Your Honor</a> ”中。两人在下面的播客中翻唱了这首歌。他们还合作翻唱了来自同一张专辑的《Razor》。</p><p>琼斯还与格罗尔一起合唱了《Flame Twin》，该歌曲取自她 2020 年专辑《Pick Me Up Off The Floor》。两人还在封面末尾插入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>的《In Bloom》。</p><p>格罗尔还演奏了喷火战机乐队的经典歌曲《Everlong》和《The Ballad of the Beaconsfield Miners》，这两首歌曲都取自开创性的专辑《Echoes, Silence, Patience &amp; Grace》。他还表演了同一张专辑中的“Statues”，这是格罗尔之前很少演奏的。 </p><p><iframe title="诺拉·琼斯与戴夫·格罗尔一起演奏（播客第 30 集）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hvmY71XWHqQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>最近的新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-shares-feelings-about-whether-nirvana-sold-out-i-didnt-feel-personally-conflicted-3518947">格罗尔出现在 Conan O&#39;Brien 的播客上</a>，谈论 Nirvana 上一张专辑《In Utero》30 周年纪念日。在那里，他详细阐述了为什么尽管 Nirvana 有着 DIY 朋克的根源，但他对 Nirvana 的财务成功并不感到“冲突”：“我认为我个人不感到冲突的原因是因为我知道乐队没有做过任何超出我们真正的自我才能到达那里，”格罗尔告诉奥布莱恩。</p><p>喷火战机目前正在巡回演出，他们邀请了几位特邀嘉宾与他们一起表演。在《Austin City Limits》中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-foo-fighters-perform-best-of-you-with-shania-twain-3511207">出人意料地亮相</a>演唱了《Best Of You》，而喷火战机<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dave-grohl-join-the-breeders-on-stage-to-cover-pixies-gigantic-3519919">乐队 (Foo Fighters)</a>随后也与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-breeders">The Breeders</a>一起登台翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixies">Pixies</a>的歌曲《Gigantic》。</p><p>乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-announce-2024-everything-or-nothing-us-stadium-tour-buy-tickets-3507831">宣布了 2024 年的体育场巡演</a>，他们将自 2015 年以来首次重返纽约花旗体育场。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/foo-fighters-tickets/artist/776005?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=1q%3AUu-yWqxyPWtJwPG1XdQ2QUkFT8Pw8CzQSQk0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272">在此处</a>找到所有门票详细信息。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-dave-grohl-play-foo-fighters-rarities-with-norah-jones-on-her-podcast-3520613">《聆听戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl) 在她的播客中与诺拉·琼斯 (Norah Jones) 一起演奏喷火战机 (Foo Fighters)》的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
